\fs28 	Ý (void)
\b adjustObject
\b0 :(id)objectToAdjust\
\
Readjusts an object in case someone changed the value while the object was in the sortedArray.\
This method simply locks the sortedArray, removes the object, inserts it again and unlocks it.\
